{"word":"G1316 - διαχωρίζομαι - diachōrízomai - dee-akh-o-rid'-zom-ahee - Depart","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διαχωρίζομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diachōrízomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-akh-o-rid'-zom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Depart</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பிரி"},{"paragraph":"to separate thoroughly or wholly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and the middle voice of <a href=\"#/G5563 - χωρίζω - chōrízō - kho-rid'-zo/5563\">G5563</a>; to <i>remove</i> (oneself) <i>wholly</i>, that is, <i>retire:</i> - depart.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}